addr="lsd-0002"
title="Monad container">monad containers</fr:link> immediately gives us <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\iota  = s]]></fr:tex> for all <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[s : S]]></fr:tex>, and hence <fr:tex
